description: Some of the world's biggest music stars have been making cameos in one another's songs. Read more at straitstimes.com.
title: Music's biggest acts play cameo
title_page: Music's biggest acts play cameo | The Straits Times
maintext:
Some of the world's biggest music stars have been making cameos in one another's songs.
American singer Selena Gomez appears in British band Coldplay's latest single and music video, Let Somebody Go, while English singer Ed Sheeran calls on his good friend, American singer Taylor Swift, for a surprise remix of his ballad, The Joker And The Queen.
